00:41:06.000 --> 00:41:11.720
So the point is that when I'm,
for example, circling this, it

00:41:11.720 --> 00:41:14.370
directs people's attention, and
then there's a permanent

00:41:14.370 --> 00:41:15.680
trace left.

00:41:15.680 --> 00:41:18.350
So you can, kind of,
do it on a slide.

00:41:18.350 --> 00:41:20.900
If you knew you were going to do
that ahead of time, you can

00:41:20.900 --> 00:41:24.870
