01:03:14.570 --> 01:03:18.860
So this solves most
of the problems.

01:03:18.860 --> 01:03:24.045
First of all, you don't have the
ghastly typesetting that

01:03:24.045 --> 01:03:25.580
you have here.

01:03:25.580 --> 01:03:27.490
The typesetting here is just
horrendous, this is sort of

01:03:27.490 --> 01:03:29.780
