typesetting.

01:03:29.780 --> 01:03:32.160
The alignment is nonexistent.

01:03:32.160 --> 01:03:35.140
There's random alignment
lines everywhere.

01:03:35.140 --> 01:03:38.560
If you look, for example, at
the way top, the yellow bar

01:03:38.560 --> 01:03:40.020
doesn't align with
anything else.

01:03:40.020 --> 01:03:42.100
The left edge of
it just doesn't

01:03:42.100 --> 01:03:43.500
align with the bullets.

01:03:43.500 --> 01:03:46.590
The open bullets are
just random.

01:03:46.590 --> 01:03:49.210
It's just a big mess,
as you pointed out.

01:03:49.210 --> 01:03:52.630
So here, just get
rid of all that.

01:03:52.630 --> 01:03:54.910
And you can do this
with any program.

01:03:54.910 --> 01:03:57.160
You can make your figure
however you want.

01:03:57.160 --> 01:04:00.240
You can put one assertion
at the top.

01:04:00.240 --> 01:04:03.430
So now assertion, another
synonym for that is "sentence

01:04:03.430 --> 01:04:06.730
headlines." So you want
your title of your

01:04:06.730 --> 01:04:08.485
slide to be a sentence.

01:04:08.485 --> 01:04:10.630
If you're not writing a
sentence, you're probably

01:04:10.630 --> 01:04:11.800
writing a topic.

01:04:11.800 --> 01:04:13.710
You're just mentioning
something-- you're giving them

01:04:13.710 --> 01:04:16.900
"what." To give "so what," you
really need a sentence.

01:04:16.900 --> 01:04:20.080
So fit a sentence of one or
two lines there, and then,

01:04:20.080 --> 01:04:22.996
give visual evidence.

01:04:22.996 --> 01:04:23.984
Yes.

01:04:23.984 --> 01:04:26.701
AUDIENCE: To sort of play
devil's advocate, I mean, I

01:04:26.701 --> 01:04:30.587
agree [INAUDIBLE], but the
advantage of having all the

01:04:30.587 --> 01:04:32.824
information on one slide is
you can see the different

01:04:32.824 --> 01:04:35.970
things, and see the different
conclusions.

01:04:35.970 --> 01:04:37.450
PROFESSOR: If you could
actually see them.

01:04:37.450 --> 01:04:39.080
The problem is, you can't
actually see all the

01:04:39.080 --> 01:04:39.960
conclusions.

01:04:39.960 --> 01:04:43.970
I agree it's nice to see all
