01:04:43.970 --> 01:04:46.910
So to do that, what I would
do is, I would make--

01:04:46.910 --> 01:04:49.820
I think there are really
three messages here--

01:04:49.820 --> 01:04:51.380
one for each of the questions.

01:04:51.380 --> 01:04:55.120
So I made a slide for the first
