01:26:44.180 --> 01:26:45.790
much you can do to help that.

01:26:45.790 --> 01:26:47.902
And students are just hosed.

01:26:47.902 --> 01:26:51.430
But try to avoid that,
mitigate it.

01:26:51.430 --> 01:26:54.244
Sometimes it seems like, just
out of habit, everyone does

01:26:54.244 --> 01:26:55.328
that 1,600-page textbook.

01:26:55.328 --> 01:26:57.850
But you could find out, what are
the actual requirements?

01:26:57.850 --> 01:26:59.440
What do people need
for [INAUDIBLE]?

01:26:59.440 --> 01:27:01.470
