be taken out.

01:27:05.554 --> 01:27:07.450
So you might have some freedom
to reduce that.

01:27:07.450 --> 01:27:10.461
The other thing is you put more
stuff in the notes, and

01:27:10.461 --> 01:27:13.898
you give the higher-level
ideas in the lecture.

