slide projector.

01:28:52.390 --> 01:28:55.820
So you only use a small
part of the room.

01:28:55.820 --> 01:28:57.700
So that's the really fundamental
problem.

01:28:57.700 --> 01:28:59.700
And if you could get around
that, it wouldn't really

01:28:59.700 --> 01:29:02.660
matter so much whether the
slides scrolled or flipped.

01:29:02.660 --> 01:29:04.215
You'd put one over there,
one over there,

01:29:04.215 --> 01:29:05.523
maybe one over there.

